 Michael Eisner
(I)


 
Producer |
 
Writer |
 
Actor





Michael Eisner was born on March 7, 1942 in Mount Kisco, New York, USA. He is a producer and writer, known for Glenn Martin DDS (2009), The Making of 'Captain Eo' (1986) and Prom Queen (2007). He has been married to Jane Breckenridge since 1967. They have three children.            
See full bio »
            
 


